Package io.github.bluelhf.anemone.gui

Class Anemone

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.bluelhf.anemone.gui.Anemone
  • public abstract class Anemone
extends Object
    Abstract base class for all Anemones. An anemone is a class that is registered via Anemones and creates dynamic inventories based on a given template and an index.
